query:
SELECT
                    attachment_id AS "attachment_id: _",
                    conversation_id AS "conversation_id: _",
                    conversation_message_id AS "conversation_message_id: _",
                    content_type AS "content_type: _",
                    status AS "status: _",
                    arrived_at AS "arrived_at: _"
                FROM attachments
                WHERE attachment_id = ?
